storyInfo: In the chaos of battle, Mostima reappears and suppresses the enemy leader with ease. However, a sandstorm appears without warning, and the Rat King appears to disperse the crowd.

attributes.content: *Pant* *pant...*
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Come on, Penguins!
attributes.name: Capone

attributes.content: Looks like you two get along great?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Grr!
attributes.name: Capone

attributes.content: What'd I ever do to you?! I'll clock you one!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Gah! Whose side are you on?!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: It- it wasn't me! It was that angel!
attributes.name: Mafioso

attributes.content: Oopsie. I missed. Seems fine though.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Get 'em, while they're—— Agh! What are you choppin' at me for?!
attributes.name: Mafioso A

attributes.content: Sorry, but I gotta stay loyal to the boss!
attributes.name: Mafioso B

attributes.content: Me too!
attributes.name: Mafioso A

attributes.content: Oh.
attributes.name: Mafioso B

attributes.content: What are you doing on the ground? Get up and fight if you ain't dead!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Y- yessir!
attributes.name: Mafioso

attributes.content: You can't be so rough with your employees. Do they at least get hazard pay?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: It's kind of hard to tell who's who. Just try to get everyone wearing black on the ground.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Hoo yeah this is a mess.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Sure is—— woah! Mostima?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: But it looks like you're all doing okay.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: When did you get here?
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: The boss called me.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Hey, it's that weird-lookin' Sankta.
attributes.name: Capone

attributes.content: Get outta here!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Somebody needs to calm down a bit.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: What are you even fighting over here? Let's all take a step back.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: She stopped the boss?!
attributes.name: Mafioso A

attributes.content: No! It's that staff! Look out, boss! She's a caster!
attributes.name: Mafioso B

attributes.content: ...Looks like we were right not to take her head on... Hey, don't get near 'em!
attributes.name: Capone

attributes.content: I ain't never seen a Sankta like you before. Or wait? Are you a Sarkaz? What the hell are you?
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: I'm just an ordinary Messenger.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Cazzata!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Grrr——
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Time for an intermission... or are you not going to listen to me?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Who do you think you are?!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: How are you all doing? It's been a long time, hasn't it?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Hey! Eyes over here!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: A couple years, I think? Maybe a couple months?
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Gah!
attributes.name: Mafioso

attributes.content: When your days are as rich and full as ours, you kinda lose track of time.
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: It's been about four years and three months, Mostima.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Yeah, that's pretty long.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Don't give me that face. If you keep looking that gloomy I'll think you've gotten sick.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Isn't this a touching reunion?!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Touching or not, it's definitely not the time to be reminiscing.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Are you really going to do it here?
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: I'll do only what needs doing.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: ...Okay. Just go easy on them.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Don't worry.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: And it looks like I've got another customer waiting.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: No matter how many times I see it, I'm always impressed how Mostima will wave her staff around all light and subtle, only to have some big amazing thing come out.
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: The mobsters're already scared stiff!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Phew. I guess I should plug a couple of them?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: What's wrong? Are we done?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: You may have some moves, but you can bet I'm not lettin' you stroll outta here.
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: You don't always have to play the big bad wolf. Just treat this as some after dinner exercise—— Hm.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Wh- what's going on? Did this fire just turn solid?
attributes.name: Mafioso

attributes.content: ...seems like Yith is around here somewhere. We better wrap this up.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Who are you monologing at? Come at me!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: You keep losing your temper. That's a really bad look for the head of a family. How are you going to keep control of the situation?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Grrr! This smug attitude of yours really pisses me off!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Arts! Take cover!
attributes.name: Mafioso

attributes.content: We'll take the Penguins. Don't wanna get in your way!
attributes.name: Mafioso

attributes.content: They're underestimating us. Show them what we can do.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: You got it! Yeeeeeeehaw!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: That's Mostima, the Messenger...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: A Messenger... are Messengers really all like this?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: ...is that the wind?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: ...wind?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Texas! Run! Quick!
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: ...Right!
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Hey! What's with the earthquake?! What did that caster just do?
attributes.name: Mafioso

attributes.content: Honestly. Old people are so impatient.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: You ain't gettin'——
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Ack——
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Hey! It's Arts! Let's get outta here!
attributes.name: Capone

attributes.content: A sandstorm? Here?
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Thing's're gettin' kinda weird.
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Texas! Over here!
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: What about Bison and Mostima? Nng!
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: The sandstorm cut them off. I'll get them!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Wait, Exusiai!
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Every time Mostima's involved, she loses control like this.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Texas! Mostima! Where are you?!
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Gah... there's sand in my eyes——
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Don't panic.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Mostima!
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Shield yourself from the sand and come with me.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: ...That's one old man we don't want to provoke within striking range.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: The ground... I'm sinking...! It's quicksand! Run! Don't get swallowed up!
attributes.name: Mafioso A

attributes.content: Boss! What do we do?!
attributes.name: Mafioso B

attributes.content: Where are they? Where's Capone?!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: They ran out under the cover of the sandstorm! We got a few of our guys in their crew...
attributes.name: Mafioso A

attributes.content: Boss! This place is gonna collapse!
attributes.name: Mafioso B

attributes.content: ...Run. We'll get another shot.
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Shit! What the hell happened?!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Another shot... hm...
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: Strange... I don't remember you having any shots left.
attributes.name: Rat King
